d><td align="center" valign="middle" >根</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >同上</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.5</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >半夏</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >天南星科</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >燥湿祛痰</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >根</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >同上</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.5</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >当归</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >伞形科</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >活血化瘀</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >根</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >同上</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >&gt; 10</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >&gt; 10</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >异烟肼</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >-</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >-</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >-</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >-</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1 μg/ml</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1 μg/ml</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表1. 29种中草药名称、传统药效、药用部位、提取方法和抗结核杆菌最小抑菌浓度</p><table-wrap id="table2" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table2">Table 2</xref></label><caption><title> Combined anti-bcg trial of 14 Chinese herbal medicines with isoniazid and rifampici</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >中草药提取物</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >浓度 (mg/mL)</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="2"  >提取物</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >+INH (0.5 μg/ml)</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >+RIF (1.6 μg/ml)</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >大蓟</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.6</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >+</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >+</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >远志</td><td align="